{%- comment -%}
  accordion-item — one <details> disclosure row (question + answer), with an
  optional leading index. Shared FAQ/accordion markup used across sections; each
  host section styles the `.accordion` / `.accordion__body` classes (and the
  inner `.idx` / `.q` / `.plus`) within its own wrapper, so every FAQ keeps its
  own look on one markup source. → COMPONENTS.md

  Params:
    question (req) — the summary text
    answer   (req) — the disclosure body (raw HTML allowed)
    index    (opt) — small leading number/label shown before the question
    open     (opt, bool) — render expanded
    attrs    (opt) — block.shopify_attributes for the Theme Editor
{%- endcomment -%}
<details class="accordion"{% if open %} open{% endif %} {{ attrs }}>
  <summary>
    {%- if index != blank -%}<span class="idx">{{ index }}</span>{%- endif -%}
    <span class="q">{{ question }}</span>
    <span class="plus">+</span>
  </summary>
  <div class="accordion__body">{{ answer }}</div>
</details>
